query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angular2-directives',
'chai',
'core-animation',
'dry',
'google-authentication',
'hashcode',
'microsoft-metro',
'monogame',
'nan',
'python-multithreading',
'traits');
